<br>
Unfortunatley, Crylin hasn't disrupted the boards enough to warrant a banning. He hasn't really done anything more than post content we dislike because of it's content, and to be honest, if we start dishing out punishment because of that, then pretty much everyone here will be banned.<br>
<br>
