<br>
<br>
o Bumping many low traffic threads with his post limit of 10.<br>
<br>
o Excessive 'de-railment' of currently 'on-topic' threads with his post limit. This is something we will not moderate for normal users, but something we will keep an eye on once this warning has been issued.<br>
<br>
o Persistant abuse / ranting in this forum, although if he wishes to discuss the matter here, I will be happy to work through our decision civily.<br>
<br>
o Posting multiple rant threads outside of the rant section with his post limit with the same content as his normal tirades.<br>
<br>
o Continued intentional disruption of the rant forum caused by any of the above, or other means of disruption that he may come up with.<br>
<br>
o Any more polls from crylin will be considered further disruption.<br>
<br>
